Imtihon IT Park tomonidan “Yosh professionallar” ittifoqi (World Skills Russia) hamda “World Skills Uzbekistan” bilan hamkorlikda tashkil etildi. Imtihon jarayonida ishtirokchilar 3 ta modul bo‘yicha o‘z ko‘nikmalarini namoyish etishdi:

